==Checklists==

The following checklist items can help make sure that effective counter-measures against XPath injection vulnerabilities have been implemented:

* [[All Input Is Validated]]
* [[Client-side Validation Is Not Relied On]]
* [[Input Is Validated for Length, Range, Format, And Type]]
* [[Valuable Information Is Not Disclosed in Error Messages]]

